@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Shipped
Shipped --> Archived : cancel
Shipped : entry / log story
Archived --> Cancelled : cancel
Cancelled --> Active : submit
Active --> Delivered : update
Delivered --> Rejected : confirm
Delivered : entry / log story
Active --> Cancelled : revert
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml